race.description: Tabtouch Supports Northam Race Club Hcp (C3)
race.comment: FAST HARRY (4) looks a progressive type on resumption for Team Williams on the back of a couple of nice trials recently. Pike was on board for those trials and remains in the saddle. 1300m first-up looks perfect, he'll be able to build into the race nicely and storm over the top to score. DEFINE BEAUTIFUL (6) finished only 1.7L at Belmont last time out and looks suited by the slight rise in trip. The inside draw should see her closer in the run however and if she runs up to recent efforts, she should be right in the finish. PURE OBSESSION (5) comes through a couple of handy trials in readiness for this and looks a nice type on return. He was a winner first-up over this trip last campaign and the inside draw is a big tick. Can resume on a positive note. HOBA METEOR (10) is another who can put her best foot forward third-up.
